The '''Senatorial Suite''' was a room of the [[Junavex Hotel]] on [[Taris/Legends|Taris]], most likely for [[Haydel Goravvus|Gorravus]]. During the [[Taris Siege|invasion of Taris]], after the loss of its [[Highpoint]] office, the Suite was the headquarters of [[The Taris Holofeed: Prime Edition|''The Taris Holofeed'']].

